gov.nih.nlm.meme.common
Interface Atom

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable, ConceptElement, CoreData, MEMEString, Rankable
All Known Implementing Classes:
Atom.Default
public interface Atom
extends MEMEString, ConceptElement

Generically represents an atomic unit of meaning in a Concept. Atoms are also known as a terms or a names. It is both the string containing the actual named thing and all of the associated information, like Codes, Sources and Termgroups, etc.

Author:
MEME Group
